title: Kxng Crooked & Dizaster Announce They Are Battling Each Other!
description:
On the heels of the announcement, Dizaster and King Crooked talk about their upcoming monumental battle event: 'The Next Episode'! Exclusive! https://www.gtxbattles.com
https://www.instagram.com/kxngcrooked/
https://www.instagram.com/mrdizaster/
https://www.instagram.com/lushoneca/
---
1:22 Lush jumps right in: "Eminem is scared to battle Dizaster! Eminem is intimidated to do it!"
7:17 Dizaster says Slaughterhouse (except Crooked) didn't want him to win and played favoritism and bias
22:19 What made Crooked finally agree to step into the arena? Says that's something he wants to do before he stops rappin kinda altogether, that's something he must do
43:00 Joe Budden and Royce was talking sh*t before they even heard the album, by the time it was out they realized there was no diss, but it was too late so they just kept on talking sh*t
50:42 Crook brought money to the table, and he was ignored by Royce and that's a betrayal to their families they must take care of
52:29 Royce blocked Crook on social media
